2 TITL Aborne, Samuel Sr- Petition for Rebecca Nurse-H40
1 _OID 2ab7b1a9-71f4-4395-9af1-e167b9549061
1 DATE Mar 1692
1 PLAC Salem, Essex, Massachusetts
1 _DSCR Source: http://salem.lib.virginia.edu/texts/tei/swp?term=abosam&div_id=n94.9&chapter_id=n94
1 _META <metadataxml><transcription>We whose nams Are heareunto subscribed being desired by goodman Nurse to declare what we knewe concerning his wives conversation for time past: we cane testyfie to all whom it may concerne that we have knowne her for: ma
2 CONC ny years and Acording to our observation her: Life and conversation was Acording to her profession and we never had Any: cause or grounds to suspect her of Any such thing as she is nowe Acused of
2 CONT 
2 CONT Samuel aborn senr</transcription></metadataxml>
