1 _META <metadataxml><cemetery /><transcription>Adam Paterson, victual dealer (grocer) residing in No.1 Rutland Street and Elizabeth Sutherland residing in West Lauriston Lane both in this parish, daughter of the late John Sutherland Officer of Excise in C
2 CONC orstophine have been three times proclaimed in order to marriage in the parish church of St Cuthbert&apos;s and no objections have been offered married on the 26 day of January (1836).........</transcription></metadataxml>
