2 CONC o drink in his house about a fortnight ago&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; a master of a voyage so drunk he could hardly speak."&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; for giving public entertainment&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; drawing wine&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; beer contrary to general cour
