2 CONC nhabitants of the River of Pascataquacke be there with content.( MPCR 1:147)&lt;/p&gt;</line><line>&lt;p&gt;Freeman: Oath of fidelity at Duxburym 1639. Robert mendum was one of those from Kittery who signed the petition to Massachusetts Bay for pro
