1 DATE 12 June 1695
1 _DSCR George HARKNESS and his wife, Christian OLIPHER, were married here on 12 June 1695. Their children, including THOMAS born 07 July 1705, were christened here. Bedrule is a hamlet 4 miles west of Jedburgh. It is also near Hawick. The original churc
2 CONC h was possibly 12th century or earlier.
