2 CONC t;span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #262626;"&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Anne Ball&lt;/span&gt; owned the convenant and was bapt. 5 Oct 1718.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&g
2 CONC t;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;This was doubtless the &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;wife of John Ball, Jr [III]&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;The same day were bapt. Children, Anne and Mary
2 CONC , and &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Martha Ball was bap. 17 Mar 1722&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</line></content></metadataxml>
