1 _OID ac4fcc8a-fb57-48c8-815f-c8bec06635a2
1 DATE 22-Oct-22 6:50:28 PM
1 _DSCR Calvin Sharman’s original copy of deed: 29 November 1800, Thomas McLaughlin Jr. to Calvin Sharman, Lots 5 and 6, in Block N, in Wentworth Division, St. David, Charlotte County, New Brunswick.
2 CONT 
2 CONT Provenance: Calvin Sharman's personal copy was handed down in the family to his great-granddaughter, Minerva Allen (Sharman) Gray (1896-2000). It was in the late 1960s that her son-in-law, Gerald L. Robbins, made this photocopy. The original deed i
2 CONC s now (2022) in the custody of Gerald's son Stanley G. Robbins.
