2 TITL Mary Butterworth Mason
1 _OID ded46121-bbcd-4373-9378-11e0837cbd5b
1 _DSCR Mary Butterworth Mason 
2 CONT 
2 CONT Memorial
2 CONT Photos
2 CONT Flowers
2 CONT Edit
2 CONT 
2 CONT 
2 CONT  Share
2 CONT  
2 CONT 
2 CONT 
2 CONT 
2 CONT Birth:  Aug. 9, 1629
2 CONT Heptonstall
2 CONT West Yorkshire, England 
2 CONT Death:  Aug. 29, 1714
2 CONT Rehoboth
2 CONT Bristol County
2 CONT Massachusetts, USA 
2 CONT 
2 CONT Mary was the daughter of Henry Butterworth and Mary "Marie" Longbottom. The family immigrated between 1630-1640 to Weymouth, Norfolk Co., MA.
2 CONT 
2 CONT On the 9th of March 1649 she married Sampson Mason. They had 13 children together:
2 CONT 
2 CONT 1)Noah b. 2 Oct 1651 Dorchester, MA and d. 2 Mar 1700. he m. (1) Martha ? and (2) Sarah Fitch
2 CONT 
2 CONT 2)Sampson Jr. b. 1654 Dorchester, MA. he m. (1) Experience Lewis and (2) Abigail Barstow.
2 CONT 
2 CONT 3)John b. 1656 Dorchester, MA and d. 18 Mar 1682. he m. Content Wales
2 CONT 
2 CONT 4)Samuel  b. 12 Feb 1657 Rehoboth, MA and d. 25 Jan 1744. he m. (1) Elisabeth Miller 
2 CONT and (2) Liddea Masters Tabor
2 CONT 
2 CONT 5)Sarah b. 15 Feb 1658 Rehoboth, MA and d. abt 28 Jan 1712. she m. (1) Samuel Phillips and (2) Daniel Brown.
2 CONT 
2 CONT 6)Mary b. 7 Feb 1660 Rehoboth, MA and d. 15 Nov 1727 Rehoboth, MA. she m. Ephraim Wheaton
2 CONT 
2 CONT 7)James b. 30 Oct 1661 Rehoboth, MA
2 CONT 
2 CONT 8)Joseph b. 6 Mar 1663 Rehoboth, MA and d. 19 May 1748. he m. (1) Anne Daggett and (2) Lydia Bowen
2 CONT 
2 CONT 9)Bethiah b. 15 Oct 1665 Rehoboth, MA and d. bef 1711. she m. John Wood
2 CONT 
2 CONT 10)Isaac b. 15 Jul 1667 Rehoboth, MA and d. 25 Jan 1742 Swansea, MA. he m. Hannah Myles
2 CONT 
2 CONT 11)Pelatiah b. 1 Apr 1669 Rehoboth, MA and d. 29 Mar 1763 Swansea, MA. he m. Hephzibah Brooks
2 CONT 
2 CONT 12)Benjamin b. 20 Oct 1670 Rehoboth, MA and d. Aug 1740. he m. Ruth Rounds
2 CONT 
2 CONT 13)Thankful b. 27 Oct 1672 Rehoboth, MA and d. aft 1730. she m. Thomas Bowen 
2 CONT  
2 CONT Family links: 
2 CONT  Parents:
2 CONT   Henry Butterworth (1602 - 1636)
2 CONT   Mary Longbotham Butterworth Clifton (1600 - 1687)
2 CONT  
2 CONT  Spouse:
2 CONT   Sampson Mason (1625 - 1676)
2 CONT  
2 CONT  Children:
2 CONT   John Mason (1657 - 1683)*
2 CONT   Samuel Mason (1657 - 1744)*
2 CONT   Mary Mason Wheaton (1660 - 1727)*
2 CONT   Joseph Mason (1663 - 1748)*
2 CONT   Isaac Mason (1667 - 1742)*
2 CONT   Pelatiah Mason (1669 - 1763)*
2 CONT   Benjamin Mason (1670 - 1740)*
2 CONT   Thankful Mason Bowen (1672 - 1745)*
2 CONT  
2 CONT  Siblings:
2 CONT   John Butterworth (1624 - 1708)*
2 CONT   Mary Butterworth Mason (1629 - 1714)
2 CONT   Patience Clifton Beere (1646 - 1692)**
2 CONT  
2 CONT *Calculated relationship
2 CONT **Half-sibling
2 CONT  
2 CONT Note: It appears that the "M.M." headstone may refer to Mary Butterworth Mason 
2 CONT   
